data.description: Don't miss this lovely  4 Bed, 1 Bath colonial home in this INCREDIBLY DESIRABLE AREA of Haddon Township! The first thing you'll notice is the charming front porch, perfect for a morning cup of coffee and a chat with friendly neighbors. The first floor features lots of light and high ceilings in the living room and dining room (which was used as a family room.) This sun-drenched home also offers a generous eat-in kitchen. The second floor features three generous bedrooms and a full bathroom. The third-floor attic space is in the midst of being transformed into a primary bedroom suite with awesome vaulted ceilings and natural light. The second bathroom is not yet installed but there is an area put aside for that to be done in the future.  Have it added yourself and reap the equity. This primary suite attic space is still waiting on sheet rock and depending on the offer, the seller will have it finished.  The walk-out basement offers storage and one of the kids had a bonus space there.  The backyard and pool are perfect for entertaining OR your own private oasis. The roof,  siding, major systems, and windows are all newer with lots of life left.  The pool was open last summer and is in good shape. Add your own cosmetic interior updates to create the perfect home in the perfect location! This home is 5 blocks from downtown shops and restaurants, and 5 blocks from Cooper River Park. Book a showing today.
